International Folklore Festival "Dani caske – Puracic " (Days of Caska - Puracic) was founded in 2011, and hosts 10-12 groups from Bosnia and Herzegovina and abroad. The Festival consists of four activities:


-       Round table on the topics of safeguarding of ICH;

-       International concerts of folk dance groups in: Puracic, Lukavac and Tuzla;

-       Gastro festival of traditional food and presentation of old and handmade crafts from BiH and visiting countries;

-       A gala concert including a parade of folklore groups, performances on the main stage, and a showcase of traditional costumes."

